OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud at first this
OL,6,Fmorning, but this breaking and
OL,7,Fclearing to give plenty of strong
OL,8,Fsunshine across the region. Feeling
OL,9,Fvery hot and humid with light winds
OL,10,Fthrough the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying very warm into the
OL,13,Fevening with some late sunshine. A
OL,14,Fvery warm and muggy night to follow,
OL,15,Fperhaps with a few mist and fog
OL,16,Fpatches.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FVery hot and humid with
OL,19,Fstrong sunshine through the day. Light
OL,20,Fwinds and continuing to feel very warm
OL,21,Finto the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
