OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FExtremely hot and humid on Thursday,
OL,7,Fparticularly in the south. Strong
OL,8,Fsunshine at times, but increasingly
OL,9,Fcloudy by Thursday with showers
OL,10,Fpossible. Becoming slightly cooler
OL,11,Ffrom Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
